Did some #backwork trying to grow my back and look like a ninja turtle.😂
Finished up with #pushups I started doing 100 push ups after every #workout.
🇺🇸@redcon1 has a #4thofjuly #sale going on with an #exclusive Totalwar flavor Click the link in my bio to take advantage of it🇺🇲
Fueled by @redcon1 
Fed by @evomealprep 
Music by @killrobbailey 
#Gym @thebarsanangelo 
Also thank you to @maximusnutritionsanangelo for, the amazing #smoothies
